<body>
Converts a boolean comparison expression <code>a</code> <small>op</small> <code>b</code> to
!( <code>a</code> <small>negop</small> <code>b</code> ). <br>
Where <small>op</small> and <small>negop</small> are mutually inverse comparison operators,
such as <code>==</code> and <code>!=</code> .
</body>
